.sn-button {
  position: relative;
}
.sn-button .unread-count {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  text-align: center;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 11px;
  line-height: 16px;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  background-color: #c00;
  color: white;
}
.sn-button .cut-number + .unread-count {
  left: calc(50% + 2px);
  top: calc(50% - 18px);
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
}
.sn-button .cut-dot + .unread-count {
  left: calc(50% + 2px);
  top: calc(50% - 14px);
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  color: transparent;
}
.sn-button .icon-email-cut-dot + .unread-count {
  left: calc(50% + 9px);
}
.sn-button .icon-bubble-cut-dot + .unread-count {
  left: calc(50% + 8px);
}
.sn-button,
.sn-stack button {
  font: inherit;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  padding: 0;
  color: #c0c0c0;
  transition: all 300ms;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.sn-button:hover,
.sn-stack button:hover,
.sn-button.active,
.sn-stack button.active {
  color: #000;
}
.sn-button .icon,
.sn-stack button .icon {
  width: 24px;
  height: 24px;
  vertical-align: middle;
}
.sn-button .icon path:not([fill]),
.sn-stack button .icon path:not([fill]),
.sn-button .icon polygon:not([fill]),
.sn-stack button .icon polygon:not([fill]),
.sn-button .icon circle:not([fill]),
.sn-stack button .icon circle:not([fill]) {
  fill: currentColor;
}
.szn-notifications .sn-button + .sn-button {
  margin-left: 16px;
}
.sn-stack {
  transform-origin: 0 0;
  padding: 0 16px;
}
.sn-stack ul {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.sn-stack ul:empty::before {
  content: "(žádná oznámení)";
  display: block;
}
.sn-stack header {
  display: flex;
  padding: 16px 0;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}
.sn-stack footer {
  padding: 16px;
  border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}
.sn-stack h2 {
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 24px;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}
.sn-stack .login-orange,
.sn-stack .login-red {
  padding: 16px 16px 32px 16px;
  text-align: center;
}
.sn-stack .login-orange h2,
.sn-stack .login-red h2 {
  font-size: 21px;
  line-height: 28px;
}
.sn-stack .login-orange p,
.sn-stack .login-red p {
  margin: 16px 0 24px 0;
  color: #6d6d6d;
}
.sn-stack .login-orange a,
.sn-stack .login-red a {
  display: block;
  height: 48px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 48px;
  font-weight: bold;
  background-color: #c00;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px -8px rgba(204, 0, 0, 0.4);
}
.sn-stack .login-orange a:hover,
.sn-stack .login-red a:hover {
  background-color: #660000;
  box-shadow: 0 12px 24px -6px rgba(204, 0, 0, 0.6);
  text-decoration: none;
}
.sn-stack.single {
  padding: 0;
}
.sn-stack.single ul {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}
.sn-stack.single li {
  box-shadow: none;
  border-radius: none;
}
.sn-stack.single li button {
  display: none;
}
.sn-stack li {
  padding: 16px;
  position: relative;
  background-color: #fff;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  border-radius: 4px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
}
.sn-stack li.clickable {
  box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 1px 4px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 16px 24px -16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}
.sn-stack li.clickable.clicked {
  box-shadow: none;
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}
.sn-stack li.clickable.clicked h3 {
  font-weight: normal;
}
.sn-stack li + li {
  margin-top: 16px;
}
.sn-stack li .blind {
  position: absolute;
  overflow: hidden;
  width: 0;
}
.sn-stack li a {
  color: inherit;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.sn-stack li h3,
.sn-stack li p {
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
}
.sn-stack li .channel-info {
  padding-left: 40px;
  padding-right: 16px;
  position: relative;
}
.sn-stack li .channel-info img {
  position: absolute;
  left: -8px;
  top: -4px;
}
.sn-stack li .channel-info h3 {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 22px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.sn-stack li .channel-info .created {
  font-size: 12px;
  line-height: 20px;
  color: #6d6d6d;
}
.sn-stack li button {
  position: absolute;
  right: 8px;
  top: 8px;
}
.sn-stack li p {
  margin-top: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 0;
}
.sn-stack li p:not(.content) {
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.sn-stack li p.content {
  color: #6d6d6d;
  line-clamp: 2;
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
}
.sn-stack li.unread .channel-info .created::after {
  content: "";
  display: inline-block;
  vertical-align: middle;
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  margin-left: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background-color: #c00;
}
.szn-notifications .sn-stack {
  position: absolute;
  overflow: auto;
  max-height: 70vh;
  border-radius: 4px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 1px 4px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 16px 24px -16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  background-color: #f8f8f8;
  width: 320px;
}
.szn-notifications .sn-stack.single {
  width: 288px;
}
.szn-notifications .sn-stack:not([hidden]) {
  animation: appear 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.25, 1.15) both;
}
@keyframes appear {
  0% {
    transform: scale(1, 0.35);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  100% {
    transform: scale(1, 1);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
.szn-notifications {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  position: relative;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 22px;
}
.szn-notifications * {
  box-sizing: inherit;
}
</style></head>
